Package com.stuypulse.stuylib.commands

Class SynchronizedCommand

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.stuypulse.stuylib.commands.SynchronizedCommand
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    edu.wpi.first.wpilibj2.command.Command
    public class SynchronizedCommand
extends java.lang.Object
implements edu.wpi.first.wpilibj2.command.Command
    A synchronized command takes in a command and synchronizes all of the methods. This can be used when a command is being passed around threads to prevent data races.
